properties.Name: DeviceEvent
properties.Description: An event type that is recorded for an device to provide a 'history' of that device using common-defined events.

Columns.Name: DeviceId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Device.

Columns.Name: DeviceEventTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Device Event Type.

Columns.Name: DeviceEventPeriodStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period start timestamp of the device event.

Columns.Name: DeviceEventPeriodEndTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period end timestamp of the device event.

Columns.Name: DeviceEventNote
Columns.Description: Notes, comments or additional information regarding the Device Event.
